name: "I Vant to Zuck..." by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Digital drawing created with a free app on an old Kindle!] This is a drawing I created on my electro-reader, which I first published on my old blog, THE PRIMITIVE ENTERTAINMENT WORKSHOP, on 25 May 2013... (That was a couple of years ago...) First tokenized TODAY, 3 Oct. 2021, on the H.E.N.! Has a nice, Halloweeny feel, even if I drew it, originally, in May. (It's always Halloween in my weird.) ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
